# --- John & Mario source archive (kept LOCAL, intentionally NOT committed) ---
# ~479 MB of migrated images plus the metadata index live alongside the site as
# a staging area for future bulk imports. Only images you actually reference
# from a post (copied into src/assets/images/) get committed to the repo.
original-blog-imgs/
blog-image-index.xlsx

# project brief (working doc, not part of the site)
BRIEF.md

# Top-level working docs (architecture, authoring, build-plan, content-model,
# design-system) live in docs/ and ARE tracked — the README points to them.
# Two exceptions stay local-only:
#   - docs/adr is a symlink to the Obsidian vault (canonical ADR store there)
#   - docs/handoff-claude-code.md is a transient process doc, not user-facing
docs/adr
docs/handoff-claude-code.md
